---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title="About — Witholi" description="Witholi is a women's health blog by Precious Oluoma, a Clinical Pharmacist on a mission to give women clinical, evidence-based answers about their bodies." />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lora:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  </head>
  <body>

    <nav>
      <div class="nav-logo"><a href="/">Witholi</a></div>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="/blog">Articles</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Topics</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://substack.com/@witholi" target="_blank">Newsletter</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>

    <main>

      <div class="page-header">
        <div class="hero-tag">About</div>
        <h1>The woman <em>behind</em> Witholi</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="photo-col">
          <div class="photo-placeholder">
            <span>Your photo here</span>
          </div>
          <div class="credentials">
            <p class="cred-name">Agbasionwe Precious Oluoma</p>
            <p class="cred-title">B.Pharm · Clinical Pharmacist</p>
            <p class="cred-school">University of Nigeria, Nsukka</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-col">
          <p class="lead">I started Witholi because I was once that woman — confused about her body, overwhelmed by her hormones, and finding nothing but generic advice that never quite fit.</p>

          <p>My name is Precious Oluoma, and I am a Clinical Pharmacist with a degree from the University of Nigeria, Nsukka. I have spent years studying how the body works — the drugs that interact with it, the hormones that drive it, the diseases that disrupt it. But it was my own personal experience with hormonal imbalance, unpredictable cycles, and the emotional chaos that comes with being a woman that made me realise something important: most women are navigating their health completely alone, with nothing but vague internet articles and well-meaning but unhelpful advice.</p>

          <p>That gap — between what women are experiencing and what they actually need to know — is exactly what Witholi exists to close.</p>

          <h2>What Witholi is about</h2>

          <p>Witholi is a women's health space built on one belief: that you deserve clinical, evidence-based answers about your own body. Not fear. Not fluff. Not a one-size-fits-all approach. Real information, explained clearly, with actionable solutions you can actually use.</p>

          <p>We cover everything that matters to a woman's body — sexual and reproductive health, hormones and the menstrual cycle, fertility, metabolic health, weight changes, chronic disease, and preventive living. We talk about medications and supplements and how they actually work inside you. We talk about food, exercise, rest, sleep, and everything in between.</p>

          <p>Because your body is not a mystery. It is speaking to you constantly. Witholi helps you learn how to listen.</p>

          <h2>Who this is for</h2>

          <p>Witholi is for every woman — young or mature — who has ever felt confused, dismissed, or overwhelmed by her own health. Whether you are trying to understand your cycle for the first time, managing a chronic condition, navigating hormonal changes, or simply trying to live better — you are welcome here.</p>

          <p>My goal is simple: I want you to leave every article feeling <em>seen</em>, <em>informed</em>, and equipped with solutions that will genuinely change things for you. Not temporarily — for good.</p>

          <div class="sign-off">
            <p>With clarity and care,</p>
            <p class="sign-name">Precious</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </main>

    <section class="newsletter">
      <div class="newsletter-inner">
        <div class="newsletter-tag">Newsletter</div>
        <h2>Get Witholi in your inbox</h2>
        <p>Evidence-informed writing on women's health, delivered straight to you. No spam, just clarity.</p>
        <a href="https://substack.com/@witholi" target="_blank" class="newsletter-btn">Subscribe on Substack →</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
      <p>© 2026 Witholi · Written with care</p>
    </footer>

  </body>
</html>

<style>
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    background: #FBF7F2;
    color: #2C2018;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1.5rem 3rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #EDE5D8;
  }

  .nav-logo a {
    font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #7C4A2D;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .nav-links a {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #6B5040;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .nav-links a:hover { color: #7C4A2D; }

  main {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 3rem;
  }

  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .hero-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #A0673A;
    background: #F5E6D3;
    padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    font-size: 2.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.25;
    color: #2C2018;
  }

  .page-header h1 em {
    color: #A0673A;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .photo-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 3/4;
    background: #EDE5D8;
    border-radius: 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: #9E7A5E;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .photo-placeholder img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 20px;
  }

  .credentials {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cred-name {
    font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #2C2018;
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }

  .cred-title {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #A0673A;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .cred-school {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #9E7A5E;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .content-col p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: #2C2018;
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.15rem !important;
    font-weight: 400 !important;
    color: #4A2E18 !important;
    font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .content-col h2 {
    font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #2C2018;
    margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem;
  }

  .content-col em {
    color: #A0673A;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .sign-off {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #EDE5D8;
  }

  .sign-off p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #6B5040;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem !important;
  }

  .sign-name {
    font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem !important;
    font-weight: 600 !important;
    color: #7C4A2D !important;
  }

  .newsletter {
    background: #F5E6D3;
    padding: 5rem 3rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .newsletter-inner {
    max-width: 580px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .newsletter-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #A0673A;
    background: #EDD5B8;
    padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .newsletter h2 {
    font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #2C2018;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .newsletter p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: #6B5040;
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .newsletter-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #7C4A2D;
    color: #FBF7F2;
    padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 40px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .newsletter-btn:hover { background: #5E3520; }

  footer {
    border-top: 1px solid #EDE5D8;
    padding: 2rem 3rem;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #9E7A5E;
  }
</style>